snippet.title: Best VGM 905 - Parasite Eve : The 3rd Birthday - Investigation of the Past
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PSP
Parasite Eve : The 3rd Birthday (2011)
Investigation of the Past
Mitsuto Suzuki
